# Complete Dev Environment Project

A well-configured development environment example.

## Installation

```bash
pip install -e ".[dev]"
```

## Development Setup

To get started with development:

```bash
# Clone and setup
git clone <repo>
cd <project>
./setup.sh

# Install dependencies
pip install -e ".[dev]"

# Run tests
make test

# Run linting
make lint
```

## Quick Start

```bash
pip install -e ".[dev]" && ./setup.sh && make test
```

See AGENTS.md for more details.
